{"tid":1205580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"獅子山已醒，睇落好精神！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-11T20:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T21:57:32.000Z","uid":97200,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"00a05e1b842bec6e43ade2f18ee8944a319188df","tid":1205580,"uid":97200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T20:45:21.000Z","msg":"6月9號 103萬人上街<br />\n港共依然我行我素 強行修例<br />\n有人覺得無用 成百萬人都做唔到咩<br />\n但正因為咁 民憤令沉睡嘅獅子慢慢睜開眼<br />\n<br />\n6月11號<br />\n警犬嚴密佈防 用力打壓市民嘅聲音<br />\n金鐘地鐵站無理截查市民<br />\n沒收市民物資 更試圖干預各學院<br />\n種種跡象表明港共有幾驚 百萬人上街未必無用<br />\n獅子啱啱先開眼 有機會瞓返 <br />\n但呢一連串打壓 仲點瞓得著？<br />\n反而激嬲獅子<br />\n<br />\n6月12號<br />\n憤怒嘅雄獅已清醒 知道瞓緊果陣邊個成日搞佢<br />\n比人搞醒又未食早餐嘅獅子會點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前未出黎嘅 歡迎你加入<br />\n已經出咗嘅 睇住身邊戰友  <br />\n幾博都好 留返份精神照顧埋附近嘅人<br />\n<br />\n今日，我地比港共、比全世界睇下<br />\n咩先係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真正獅子山精神</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 不散</span></span>"},{"pid":"9889c662bbb47375d3b67a250b54d4353745b409","tid":1205580,"uid":258217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T20:46:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad6d7a8df53b5e054df85921512aab3cc06d49d5","tid":1205580,"uid":73572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T21:13:10.000Z","msg":"寫得咁好就唔好加密啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf651c49a3faf7db2750bee83b9f7abb205eefc4","tid":1205580,"uid":252203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T21:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d54ffb8978bc76c4f8444ae32efb2a65af3f15","tid":1205580,"uid":97200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad6d7a8df53b5e054df859215